==English==

===Etymology===
First employed by Vietnamese Zen Buddhist teacher Thich Nhat Hanh (b. 1926).  In 1966 Thich Nhat Hanh founded the Order of Interbeing.

===Noun===
'''interbeing'''

# {{religion}} A state of [[connect]]edness and [[interdependence]] of all [[phenomena]].

